(4. CLForm ? Form) Tj
T*
T*
(CLForm crea form accessibili con campi comuni, help/error, method spoof e upload) Tj
T*
(file \(enctype automatico\).) Tj
T*
T*
/F2 10.00 Tf
14.00 TL
(```) Tj
T*
($form = \(new CLForm\(\)\)) Tj
T*
(->start\('/contact/submit','POST',['id'=>'contact-form']\)) Tj
T*
(->csrf\('_token','ABC123'\)) Tj
T*
(->text\('name','Nome',['required'=>true,'placeholder'=>'Mario Rossi']\)) Tj
T*
(->email\('email','Email',['required'=>true,'help'=>'Non condivideremo la tua email.']\)) Tj
T*
(->textarea\('message','Messaggio',['rows'=>5,'required'=>true]\)) Tj
T*
(->checkbox\('privacy','Accetto la privacy',['required'=>true]\)) Tj
T*
(->submit\('Invia'\)->reset\('Annulla'\);) Tj
T*
(echo $form;) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
T*
/F1 11.00 Tf
16.00 TL
(? Campi:) Tj
T*
(  text/email/password/number/date/tel/url/file/hidden/textarea/select/radioGroup/checkbox.) Tj
T*
(? select: supporta placeholder e optgroup; usa 'value' \(o array per multiple\).) Tj
T*
(? radioGroup: choices come ['val'=>'Etichetta']; 'inline'=>true per layout) Tj
T*
(  orizzontale.) Tj
T*
(? Sicurezza: escaping di default; per innerHTML usa 'raw'=>true \(solo se fidato\).) Tj
T*
(? Method spoof: ->methodSpoof\('PUT'|'PATCH'|'DELETE'\) aggiunge hidden _method.) Tj
T*
T*
T*
/F3 14.00 Tf
18.00 TL
(5. CLButton ? Pulsanti) Tj
T*
T*
/F1 11.00 Tf
16.00 TL
(CLButton genera pulsanti singoli o gruppi \(toolbar\) con varianti e icone, inclusi) Tj
T*
(link-as-button e stato loading.) Tj
T*
T*
/F2 10.00 Tf
14.00 TL
(```) Tj
T*
(\(new CLButton\(\)\)->single\('Salva', ['variant'=>'primary','size'=>'md']\);) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(// Gruppo unito) Tj
T*
(echo \(new CLButton\(\)\)) Tj
T*
(->startGroup\(['merge'=>true]\)) Tj
T*
(->button\('Indietro',['variant'=>'ghost']\)) Tj
T*
(->submit\('Salva',['variant'=>'success']\)) Tj
T*
(->button\('Elimina',['variant'=>'danger']\)) Tj
T*
(->render\(\);) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
T*
/F1 11.00 Tf
16.00 TL
(? Varianti: primary, secondary, outline, ghost, success, danger.) Tj
T*
(? Taglie: sm, md, lg; full width con 'full'=>true.) Tj
T*
(? Icone: passa HTML raw in 'iconLeft'/'iconRight' \(SVG o emoji\).) Tj
T*
(? Link: ->link\('Testo','/url', [...]\) con role='button'.) Tj
T*
T*
T*
/F3 14.00 Tf
18.00 TL
